    "dominantPhase": "Mid Game",
    "description": "Lolita is serviceable early with point-and-click engage (dash + stun) and strong lane/roam protection from shields, but her fight-winning value jumps when Noumenon Blast is available for large-area stuns. Mid game is her best window as teamfights start and projectile denial becomes decisive; late she remains impactful with ult threat and peel, though she can be outscaled by damage and needs items to survive extended fights."
